#CircuitBreakerSG D-29
Didn't know what to cook for lunch and suddenly saw @xxjamboreexx's fried rice. Quickly cooked rice and here's my Garlicky Fried Rice with Egg & the remaining half piece of Bak Kwa. Topped with herbed Pork Chop. Simple yet satisfying 😊

Happy lunching!
